Package: openxcom
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
	timidity
Suggests: openxcom-data
Description: Classic turn-based strategy game
 UFO: Enemy Unknown (X-COM: UFO Defense in USA) is a popular
 strategy video game made by Mythos / Microprose, where you
 take control of the X-COM organization to fight off the alien
 menace invading Earth.
 OpenXcom is an open-source clone of that game,
 licensed under the GPL and written in C++ / SDL.
 IMPORTANT: OpenXcom requires game resources from original
 game (DOS, Windows or Steam version).
